data.description: Beautiful Move in Ready One Story home in Gated/Guarded Villages of La Canada. Well maintained home is move in ready. Beautiful 3 bedroom/2 bath with 2 year old HVAC unit and No Poly pipes. Large kitchen with island and dining area opening to great room or formal dining area. Very versatile spacious floor plan. All bedrooms have large Walk In closets. Lots of cabinets and pull outs & pantry. Master with double sinks and walk in shower. All in Neutral Colors. All lights are Low Power inset LED. Large laundry room. Low care landscaping with automatic drip timer front/back. Nighthawk Carbon Detector installed in Laundry Room. This gated community also has a guard on duty, walking trails, Childrens Play Park and Lighted streets. Adjacent to El Conquistador golf course and close to shopping.
